@startuml
title UC11 - Use Chatbot Sequence
actor User
participant "Web UI" as UI
participant "Chatbot API" as API
participant "Chatbot Service" as Svc
participant "AI Provider Client" as AIClient
cloud "Chatbot/AI Provider" as AI
database "DB" as DB
User -> UI : Ask question
UI -> API : POST /chatbot/messages
API -> Svc : answer(userId, message)
Svc -> DB : load safe user/match context
Svc -> AIClient : send prompt and context
AIClient -> AI : REST JSON
AI --> AIClient : response
AIClient --> Svc : answer
Svc -> DB : save conversation if configured
Svc --> API : ChatbotResponse
API --> UI : 200 OK
UI --> User : Show answer
@enduml
